FeedPackage.Description: NGinn.BPM is an open-source BPM engine for Microsoft.Net and Mono. It contains a process modeling language and a workflow execution engine that can run embedded or standalone. NGinn.BPM is inspired by YAWL and BPMN, process model is based on Petri nets. The execution engine is transactional, based on asynchronous messaging/ESB concepts.
FeedPackage.ReleaseNotes: Initial nuget, this is a development version not intended for use in production.
